OL,3,CMinister backs plans for 42 sheltered
OL,4,Chomes after appeal
OL,6,FPlans for more than 40 sheltered
OL,7,Fhousing units at St Joseph's Care Home
OL,8,Fin St Helier have been approved on
OL,9,Fappeal.
OL,11,FThe proposed development of 38 one-bed
OL,12,Fand four two-bed homes for those aged
OL,13,Fover 55 within gardens to the east and
OL,14,Fsouth of the existing main building
OL,15,Fhas proved controversial, but Jersey's
OL,16,FEnvironment Minister has agreed to
OL,17,Fgive it the green light.
