OL,3,CMinister backs plans for 42 sheltered
OL,4,Chomes after appeal
OL,6,FThe application was originally
OL,7,Frejected by the island's Planning
OL,8,FCommittee back in July due to concerns
OL,9,Fabout overdevelopment harming the
OL,10,Farea's character and a "substantial
OL,11,Floss" of green space that it said was
OL,12,F"not demonstrably outweighed by an
OL,13,Foverall community benefit".
OL,15,FHowever, following an appeal by the
OL,16,Fcare home, an independent planning
OL,17,Finspector reviewed the case and
OL,18,Frecommended it should be allowed to go
OL,19,Fahead.
