OL,3,CMinister backs plans for 42 sheltered
OL,4,Chomes after appeal
OL,6,FPhilip Staddon highlighted there was a
OL,7,F"substantial number of objections from
OL,8,Fmembers of the public", but that
OL,9,F"extra care housing for older people
OL,10,Fis needed and desirable in Jersey".
OL,12,FHe added: "It reflects the policy
OL,13,Fapproach of 'rightsizing' and has the
OL,14,Fpotential to not only provide
OL,15,Fislanders with appropriate quality
OL,16,Faccommodation for later years, but
OL,17,Falso to free up larger properties for
OL,18,Ffamily occupation."
