OL,3,CMinister backs plans for 42 sheltered
OL,4,Chomes after appeal
OL,6,FMr Staddon recognised that planning
OL,7,Fjudgements are complex, but concluded
OL,8,Fthe proposed development would not
OL,9,Fsignificantly harm the landscape and
OL,10,Fis in line with the Bridging Island
OL,11,FPlan.
OL,13,FHis recommendation to support the
OL,14,Fchanges has now been accepted by
OL,15,FEnvironment Minister, Deputy Steve
OL,16,FLuce, who adds: "This decision
OL,17,Freflects the importance of providing
OL,18,Fhigh-quality housing options for older
OL,19,Fislanders.
