OL,3,CMinister backs plans for 42 sheltered
OL,4,Chomes after appeal
OL,6,F"The development at St Joseph's Care
OL,7,FHome will help meet a clear need for
OL,8,Fsheltered accommodation, supporting
OL,9,Four policy of rightsizing and ensuring
OL,10,Fthat people can live comfortably and
OL,11,Findependently in later life.
OL,13,F"It also demonstrates that, with
OL,14,Fcareful design and planning, we can
OL,15,Fdeliver new homes without compromising
OL,16,Fthe character of our island."
